{
  "stem": "3933.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I went, I came home and I told my mother-in-law.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she say, of course, I told you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "One of those days you be in trouble, you're stubborn.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This is one incident.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We're going now in the ghetto, going to work, and everybody was-- very few-- there were quite a few were working for them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was a [NON-ENGLISH] a factory they opened to-- to sew uniforms, and-- and fix uniforms and sew uniforms.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There were very quite a few Jews employed there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we'd say to ourselves, no they need us, there is so little left, they need us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we were hoping, living with hope, and going on with our lives.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Jewish people, they take programs in the history of Jews, and they always survive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You know how it is.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The poles-- started climbing the poles, the soldiers, the German soldiers, and fixing something there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't like it, because there was no electricity in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we said, something is not like this, or kosher.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we heard the old stories-- somebody came in and said, yes they are taking us during the night.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They will cleaning-- cleaning-- going to clean us out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And everybody who has a some of their friend, a Gentile friend.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You have somebody you know, somebody you used to go to school, somebody, some-- and the truth of the matter is, they were punished.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Polack who's going-- going to hide you was punished almost same way-- deadly.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Which in way, in a way I explain it, I don't blame them, but whatever opportunities they could, and they would, and they even helped out.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now I've got a friend, his name was Kola, which comes from Nikolai.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Kola, K-O-L-A.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I know him, he was a Polack.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
